TeacherUnit:
	UNIT YoungTeacher Veteran 0x40 Level(10,Ally,False)     [2,13] 0b 0x0 0x1 REDA3R14 [IronLance,SteelBlade] [0x0,0x0,0x0,0x0]
	UNIT
	
